OL,3,CAirport director 'hopeful' runway
OL,4,Cclosures will end by autumn
OL,6,FThe director of Ronaldsway Airport
OL,7,Fsaid he hopes all runway closures will
OL,8,Fbe lifted "towards the back end of
OL,9,Fsummer", following months of daily
OL,10,Fbreaks.
OL,12,FSince August 2023 the runway closes
OL,13,Fdaily in the morning between the hours
OL,14,Fof 08:30 and 09:05, and 11:00 and
OL,15,F11:35 due to staffing shortages.
OL,17,FGary Cobb said the situation at the
OL,18,Fisland's airport has improved in the
OL,19,Fpast year, but the air traffic control
OL,20,Ftower is still not operating at full
OL,21,Fcapacity.
