OL,3,CAirport director 'hopeful' runway
OL,4,Cclosures will end by autumn
OL,6,FGary said: "We still continue at two
OL,7,Fbreaks, the two morning breaks. That
OL,8,Fwill continue, but we will just then
OL,9,Fexit all of the breaks in one go.
OL,11,F"So you won't see a lessening of that.
OL,12,FIt will just be a complete removal of
OL,13,Fthe breaks. And again, I'm hopeful
OL,14,Fthat towards the back end of summer is
OL,15,Fa position that we can do."
OL,17,FA total of 18 air traffic controllers
OL,18,Fare required to lift all runway
OL,19,Fclosures, and the airport is currently
OL,20,Foperating at 17.
