OL,6,FGary said: "The big issue now will be
OL,7,Fthe training of these air traffic
OL,8,Fcontrollers.
OL,10,F"We could actually go out and get the
OL,11,F18 now, but as we've got so many
OL,12,Fpeople in training, they would
OL,13,Factually be sat around waiting for a
OL,14,Ftraining seat.
OL,16,F"So we've made that conscious choice
OL,17,Fnot to go for the 18th yet.
